{"tid":1793532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱同藍絲親戚食飯屌到佢地跪喺度喊","createTime":"2019-12-22T12:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T04:38:59.000Z","uid":150100,"like":133,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5483fdf16718956a625183b036bb4b1d0a0d512a","tid":1793532,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:50:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n話說今日冬至啦<br />\n咁就跟傳統出嚟食飯啦<br />\n食食下啲親戚就嚟料啦<br />\n都係話咩廢青暴徒搞事嗰啲啦<br />\n咁我開頭都忍住啦<br />\n點知佢越講越離譜啦<br />\n我就終於忍唔住一嘢拍落張枱度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你地同我跪喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依一喝可以話驚天地，泣鬼神<br />\n加埋拍枱拍爆曬啲碗嘅效果<br />\n班親戚即刻嚇到跪咗喺度<br />\n仲開始流馬尿啦<br />\n之後我就一路屌鳩佢地<br />\n一路幫隻手止血啦<br />\n屌到咁上下發現止唔到血就嗱嗱聲走<br />\n反正班垃圾屌嚟都嘥氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好型"},{"pid":"da0827550d704a9c8624bea98ef2e9291cf04cc8","tid":1793532,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:50:28.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【置頂】【行動po求推】好㷫呀！警曱向人群舉槍，聽日同我即刻行動。而嚟緊嘅行動係1223stuck稅局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%